title: Souka no Ori
sinopse:
Orphan Yuzuha's days of normal take a sharp left turn into peculiar when one day, Yuzuha receives an invite from a horrendously rich family. As instructed, she presents herself at Karyuin manor where she is greeted by brothers Aoi and Tsubaki who seem to know her...

(Source: huamulan03)
